{"tid":798020,"cid":18,"subCid":0,"title":"華盛頓大學：男人睇野快過女人唔係好事","createTime":"2018-08-29T03:47:11.000Z","updateTime":"2018-08-30T10:27:53.000Z","uid":165773,"like":0,"dislike":9,"uniUserReply":13,"replies":[{"pid":"f9f8379445c85cfef533948f062b1e6616b0a41b","tid":798020,"uid":165773,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2018-08-29T03:47:11.000Z","msg":"Men and women process motion at different speeds <a href=\"https://www.futurity.org/men-women-visual-processing-motion-1850612/\" data-sr-url=\"https://r.lihkg.com/link?u=https%3A%2F%2Fwww.futurity.org%2Fmen-women-visual-processing-motion-1850612%2F&d=vRx0i4A9Lt2JCJ9PTFs9w26tz0R9Svbxs0EcWe5CwMI%3D&h=86e03bfa\" data-auto-link target=\"_blank\">https://www.futurity.org/men-women-visual-processing-motion-1850612/</a><br />\n<br />\n研究員比250個男人女人望電腦螢幕一條黑bar 幾時突然由左移去右<br />\n男人平均用十分之一秒甚至更短就判斷倒<br />\n女人平均慢男人25%-75%<br />\n<br />\n研究員表示男人快唔一定係好事<br />\n因爲之前研究顯示<br />\n愈自閉、抑鬱、年老<br />\n平均時間愈快<br />\n因為腦部制約訊號能力較低"},{"pid":"cd7a6dcbe49a0a7c645076cf374e5d5907db1cd4","tid":798020,"uid":36296,"like":38,"dislike":1,"score":37,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2018-08-29T03:49:55.000Z","msg":"個研究女人做架？"},{"pid":"a9bb1b901c807b35f615d53239e307bf3cc315f2","tid":798020,"uid":9736,"like":12,"dislike":0,"score":12,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2018-08-29T03:50:57.000Z","msg":"反應快又係衰"},{"pid":"7a2e5d193c759db9332eac6fa76b6ad7e4b18519","tid":798020,"uid":73910,"like":31,"dislike":0,"score":31,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2018-08-29T03:53:52.000Z","msg":"唔怪得轉綠燈時，過左半條馬路d女人先開始起步<img src=\"/assets/faces/dog/smile.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"d0c42fee4f6b54981a47838ba4c3092a3bf9b164","tid":798020,"uid":37869,"like":8,"dislike":0,"score":8,"quote":{"pid":"7a2e5d193c759db9332eac6fa76b6ad7e4b18519","tid":798020,"uid":73910,"like":31,"dislike":0,"score":31,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2018-08-29T03:53:52.000Z","msg":"唔怪得轉綠燈時，過左半條馬路d女人先開始起步<img src=\"/assets/faces/dog/smile.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2018-08-29T07:09:24.0